{
  "stem": "4963.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Somehow I-- it was just a feeling all along that I will survive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think that's more or less, I mean, when I think about it now and I have my grandchildren who are the same age, 11, 10, and they were children.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I was never a child, I knew exactly what I had to do, how I-- how I should do it, and I think that's what really-- one of the reasons for my survival.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because you can imagine being without parents and having to-- and as much as my aunts were nice to me, they were really, you know, their first obligation was to their own children to-- for survival-- so I had to worry-- fend for myself.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So here you are in this workforce.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How did you join the workforce?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I immediately-- well, my uncle helped me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Again, without my uncle's help I would have never been able to-- to organize the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so I went, you know, and I immediately took out my-- but I had to do all the thinking for myself, you know, because there was nobody.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Once I went out in the workforce, nobody there to help me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I had immediately taken off the [INAUDIBLE] or the star from my left side from the back, and then quickly took off the one from the left, from the front, and was just looking out, watching out where I could throw myself in with a Lithuanian group, which I did.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I found a place and then--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I recognized it, and it was close to-- to [INAUDIBLE] where my home was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I went over there to-- to these people's home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember the name now.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
